Recent changes (JGH):
-Changed player paddle material to glass so ball can be seen through it
-Added scoring if ball goes past +/-400
-Reset ball to middle after a score

Recent changes (SJ+JGH):
-Added PaddleAI which follows the ball along the Z and Y access based on a changeable speed.
-Added Ball that bounces between the paddles.
-Added limitations for the paddles and ball so they are limited within a certain distance in all directions.
